{
    "name": "brokendoll",
    "description": "BrokenDoll: aggressive mob with two weapons (primary + aoe). SelfDestructSystem handles the suicide countdown out-of-band: when active it freezes velocity, so the tree keeps trying to attack but the body stays put until the fuse runs out and the entity explodes.",
